jabberd2 (2.1.16-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * new upstream
  * don't use dpatch anymore
  * move <filter> inside <aci> (bug in upstream) (formerly dpatch)
  * add entry for the fs storage driver (formerly dpatch)
  * make path names more sensible in example config files (formerly dpatch)
  * switch to GnuSASL
  * add stats dir
  * switch to PAM authentication as default
  * switch to BerkeleyDB as default storage
  * fix start stop scripts. add --oknodo to start-stop-daemon

 --  Harald Braumann <harry@unheit.net>  Wed, 26 Sep 2007 17:44:06 +0200

